import axios from "axios" import { useEffect, useState } from "react" import { fetchingStudentsList } from "./api/AddNewStudentService" export default function StudentListComponent() { const[message, setMessage] = useState(null) const[students,setStudents] = useState([]) useEffect ( () => handleSubmit() ) function handleSubmit(){ fetchingStudentsList() .then((response) => successResponse(response)) .catch((error) => errorResponse(error)) .finally(()=> console.log('cleanup')) } function successResponse(response){ setStudents(response.data) setMessage('Students List') } function errorResponse(response){ console.log(response) } return (
